<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٣٧ ... سُورَةُ الصَّافَّاتِ ... آياتها ١٨٢ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالصَّافَّاتِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ حِينَ تَصُفُّ فيِ عِبَادَتِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَالزَّاجِرَاتِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ حِينَ تَزْجُرُ السَّحَابَ، وَتَسُوقُهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَالتَّالِيَاتِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالمَلَائِكَةِ حِينَ تَتْلُو ذِكْرَ اللهِ، وَكَلَامَهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّارِدٍ}</span> ... جِنِّيًّ مُتَمَرِّدٍ، خَارجٍ عَنِ الطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيُقْذَفُونَ}</span> ... يُرْجَمُونَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دُحُورًا}</span> ... طَرْدًا لِلشَّيَاطِينِ عَنِ الاِسْتِمَاعِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاصِبٌ}</span> ... دَائِمٌ مُوجِعٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَطِفَ الْخَطْفَةَ}</span> ... اخْتَلَسَ الكَلِمَةَ؛ مُسَارَقَةً بِسُرْعَةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شِهَابٌ}</span> ... مَا يُرَى كَالكَوْكَبِ يَنْقَضُّ مِنَ السَّمَاءِ بِسُرْعَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ثَاقِبٌ}</span> ... مُضِيءٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَلَقْنَاهُم}</span> ... خَلَقْنَا أَبَاهُمْ آدَمَ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّازِبٍ}</span> ... لَزِجٍ يَلْتَصِقُ بَعْضُهُ بِبَعْضٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دَاخِرُونَ}</span> ... صَاغِرُونَ، أَذِلَّاءُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَجْرَةٌ}</span> ... نَفْخَةٌ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{احْشُرُوا}</span> ... اجْمَعُوا.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَزْوَاجَهُمْ}</span> ... نُظَرَاءَهُمْ، وَقُرَنَاءَهُمْ فيِ الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>